Interface Summary
CacheRasterDataSource.CacheStore Cache store interface.
ImageFilterRasterDataSource.ImageFilter Interface for bitmap filtering
RasterDataSource Interface for all raster tile data sources.

Class Summary
AbstractRasterDataSource Abstract base class for raster datasources.
CacheRasterDataSource Data source for caching and fast retrieval of source tiles.
HTTPRasterDataSource Base class for online tile data sources that use HTTP connection for transport.
ImageFilterRasterDataSource Data source for processing (filtering) source tile images.
PackagedRasterDataSource A raster data source that uses the map bundled in the /res/raw/ folder as a source.
StreamRasterDataSource An abstract base class for stream-based raster data sources.
